data.title: Lindsey Pollock Home Page, University of South Australia
data.meta_description: Professional home page for Ms Lindsey Pollock, Operations Lead: Enterprise Partnerships,  Enterprise Partnerships Unit,  University of South Australia
data.text:
Lindsey Pollock is the Operations Lead: Enterprise Partnerships. Lindsey leads the operations of UniSA’s Enterprise Hub.

Lindsey is an experienced event design and management professional with a passion for crafting the perfect experience to meet the strategic aim of the event. Over the years, she’s accumulated diverse event experience, from large-scale public events to venue and concert management, community events, fundraising activities, and university student recruitment events and engagements. Her work style is adaptable so her work has allowed her to work in many industries from arts and creative, to healthcare, higher education, not-for-profit and corporate.
